full_title: FRIED by ¥$, Kanye West & Ty Dolla $ign
title: FRIED

description.plain:
“Fried” was first revealed at the Vultures 2 listening party on March 8, 2024. The song was also played during the March 12th listening party held in San Francisco and during Ty Dolla $ign’s birthday party on April 13th.

The song was also previewed at the BRED Festival Abu Dhabi on April 27th by Ty Dolla $ign during his set.
